{"tid":2161403,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【黃世澤談總辭】：最戀棧權力就係熱狗呀，焦土呀果啲人","createTime":"2020-08-17T13:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T15:32:16.000Z","uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14e643361cd32e1603efbcb6c3cb56fcc339bf92","tid":2161403,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"8:20<br />\n最戀棧權力最在意權力就係熱狗呀，焦土呀果啲人<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cykKszumbeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcykKszumbeg&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21IeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=7a6d1a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cykKszumbeg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12:00<br />\n呢件事我唯一信就係信soloman yue, 其他人唔好亂咁解釋<br />\n叫我搵袁弓夷合作既留言我全部ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n13:50<br />\n老蕭講新加玻唔好亂UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔熟書就唔應該拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我聽左成段<br />\n我覺得最唔撚熟書既就係佢<br />\n佢成段叫人留任得2個考慮<br />\n1. 戰略合理性考慮,  要用rational方法去達到成功, 入去做到癱瘓議會就OK<br />\n2. 留任有無涉及大是大非既問題<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪唔知改撚左議事規則, 拉布都可以俾人踢出議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n癱瘓議會癱條毛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成段廿分鐘主要都係用屌熱狗垃圾黎做論據去支持泛民留任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁同美國班撚屌話投joe biden原因為because he is not trump有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n論據空泛, 呢D政治評論員食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e919233539b89315b3a4cd84ad011c09193203e","tid":2161403,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"留同唔留，同樣都係有利有弊。<br />\n<br />\n留者，有班議員，點都可以保護手足（如果許智峯唔係議員，晨早俾黑警拆骨）。又或者可以用公務探訪，去監獄關心手足情況。<br />\n<br />\n當然留最大問題，就係會做成分化。我地行到今日，靠既就係團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458dc23b958a22af86c5f6b78a6b22359e518344","tid":2161403,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4e919233539b89315b3a4cd84ad011c09193203e","tid":2161403,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"留同唔留，同樣都係有利有弊。<br />\n<br />\n留者，有班議員，點都可以保護手足（如果許智峯唔係議員，晨早俾黑警拆骨）。又或者可以用公務探訪，去監獄關心手足情況。<br />\n<br />\n當然留最大問題，就係會做成分化。我地行到今日，靠既就係團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"係咪訓左半年<br />\n鄺仔近排果次咪俾人直接推低捉走　野都講唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係佢地無咁大機會被起訴，可以無成本重覆俾人拘捕多幾次<br />\n做多幾單新聞，畫面靚囉又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家檔唔到架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋鄺仔都唔再出黎啦而家"},{"pid":"b8e6c559ef5b3f2f8bf146ee690500e8eee4eaea","tid":2161403,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"8e1f2dac9a6d5267ac891feb4f02b58248e5cb3e","tid":2161403,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"其實有第三條路行<br />\n政事台討論中"},{"pid":"8591fcd443a0607bcad9dd95daa0a9b04369dda0","tid":2161403,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"458dc23b958a22af86c5f6b78a6b22359e518344","tid":2161403,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4e919233539b89315b3a4cd84ad011c09193203e","tid":2161403,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"留同唔留，同樣都係有利有弊。<br />\